LEATHA M. FREEMAN v. JAMES T. VOCELLE, as Director of the State Beverage Department of the State of Florida. 33 So. (2nd) 602 January 23, 1948

January Term, 1948

Division B Thomas H. Anderson, for petitioner. Patton and Kanner, for respondent. PER CURIAM:

The answer to the question propounded is denied because the question does not come within the purview of Rule 38 of this Court.

THOMAS, C. J., BUFORD, ADAMS and BARNS, JJ., concur.
